angel investors, venture capitalists,

5
00:00:12,570 --> 00:00:13,850
accelerators and incubators.

6
00:00:13,850 --> 00:00:17,240
Each of these options have their
own benefits and downsides.

7
00:00:17,240 --> 00:00:19,310
We'll spend some time
going over each of them.

8
00:00:19,310 --> 00:00:20,940
You'll also hear from entrepreneurs and

9
00:00:20,940 --> 00:00:24,110
